### Component Composition
- FooterLinks: Grid of footer sections with links
- SocialLinks: Social media icon buttons
- Additional elements: Country selector, copyright notice

### Styling Classes
- Footer: `w-full border-t border-gray-200 mt-12`
- Container: `max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-10 flex flex-col gap-8`
- Content: `flex items-start justify-between gap-8 flex-wrap`
- Sidebar: `min-w-[260px] space-y-4`
- Copyright: `text-xs text-gray-500`

### Layout Structure
- Full width footer with subtle top border
- Constrained content container
- Two-column layout with responsive wrapping
- Copyright notice at bottom

## Layout Specifications

### Container System
- Max width: `max-w-7xl` (1280px) - matches Header
- Centering: `mx-auto`
- Horizontal padding: `px-4` (16px)
